evidence_text: Silencing the expression of the catalytic subunit of DNA-PK (DNA-PKcs) increased sensitivity to cisplatin and decreased the appearance of yH2AX after cisplatin treatment.
qualifying_text: SNVs should be loss-of-function and associated with drug sensitivity. However, not all SNVs may result in loss-of-function.
